♫ I can fly to the moon ♫

696
01:02:06,190 --> 01:02:10,510
♫ I can fly to the stars ♫

697
01:02:10,510 --> 01:02:18,280
♫ Will I see the end of the dark sky that's hiding? ♫

698
01:02:18,280 --> 01:02:22,170
♫ I can fly to the moon ♫

699
01:02:22,170 --> 01:02:26,190
♫ I can fly to the stars ♫

700
01:02:26,190 --> 01:02:35,550
♫ The night feels like a lie. It's hidden inside. ♫

701
01:02:35,550 --> 01:02:43,440
♫ I followed the dark path without purpose ♫

702
01:02:43,440 --> 01:02:51,450
♫ Could it be better than to be abandoned by the world? ♫

703
01:02:51,450 --> 01:02:55,190
♫ On top of the white burnt ashes ♫

704
01:02:55,190 --> 01:02:59,710
♫ My future that was engraved in struggles ♫

705
01:02:59,710 --> 01:03:03,630
[My Happy Ending]

706
01:03:03,630 --> 01:03:04,950
How about the custody?

707
01:03:04,950 --> 01:03:06,730
The husband is mostly in charge of childcare.

708
01:03:06,730 --> 01:03:09,870
He could end up getting the custody, too.

709
01:03:09,870 --> 01:03:13,130
Just one thing. I just need one thing.

710
01:03:14,550 --> 01:03:18,930
If I can't even fulfill my desire to become a good parent...

711
01:03:18,930 --> 01:03:21,370
I'll do what you want.

712
01:03:21,370 --> 01:03:22,770
I think it's for the better.

713
01:03:22,770 --> 01:03:24,770
Sunbae, have you always been like this?

714
01:03:24,770 --> 01:03:27,420
Isn't this good for you, too?

715
01:03:27,420 --> 01:03:29,850
The reason you joined Dereve.

716
01:03:30,850 --> 01:03:32,530
Does Jae Won also know?
